	<h2>
			CNV pede que a PF acompanhe investigação sobre a morte de Malhães		</h2>








        <div style="clear:both;"></div>
        <div class="itp-share">

                	<a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-url="http://cnv.memoriasreveladas.gov.br/outros-destaques/476-cnv-pede-que-a-pf-acompanhe-investigacao-sobre-a-morte-de-malhaes.html" data-text="CNV pede que a PF acompanhe investiga&ccedil;&atilde;o sobre a morte de Malh&atilde;es" data-via="" data-lang="pt" data-size="small" data-related="" data-hashtags="" data-count="none"><img src="file://///mecsrv01/portalmec_dev/www/cnv/site/templates/cnv/images/btn_twitter.png" />Tweet</a><div class="itp-share-fbl">
            <iframe src="//www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=http%3A%2F%2Fcnv.memoriasreveladas.gov.br%2Foutros-destaques%2F476-cnv-pede-que-a-pf-acompanhe-investigacao-sobre-a-morte-de-malhaes.html&amp;send=0&amp;locale=pt_BR&amp;layout=button_count&amp;show_faces=false&amp;width=90&amp;action=like&amp;colorscheme=light&amp;height=25" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" style="border:none; overflow:hidden; width:90px; height:25px;" allowTransparency="true"></iframe>
